    "TranslationIn today's era of accelerated communication and internet advancements, the exponential growth of information and increasing global interconnectivity have accentuated the challenges of language barriers.",
    "Consequently, the demand for machine translation is on the rise.",
    "Within the ongoing wave of artificial intelligence, machine translation theory, technology, and future prospects have attracted high interest.Machine translation involves the transformation of grammatical structures to align with the target language, followed by the translation of individual words from the source language to the target language.",
